                Designed for structured academic workflows, event governance, and student engagement.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                <div class="logo-chip">Student Affairs</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                <div class="logo-chip">Campus Life</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                <div class="logo-chip">Academic Events</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-6">
                <div class="logo-chip">Student Clubs</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-spacing reveal-on-scroll">
    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="quote-mark mb-3">“</div>
                <p class="subtle-text">
                    The organizer dashboard makes it easier to manage submissions, monitor approvals, and track event participation.
                </p>
                <div class="data-label mt-3">Organizer Experience</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="quote-mark mb-3">“</div>
                <p class="subtle-text">
                    Staff can quickly review pending events and keep the approval workflow clean and organized.
                </p>
                <div class="data-label mt-3">Staff Coordinator Experience</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="quote-mark mb-3">“</div>
                <p class="subtle-text">
                    Students can discover approved activities, register with fewer steps, and manage participation easily.
                </p>
                <div class="data-label mt-3">Student Experience</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section-spacing reveal-on-scroll">
    <div class="cta-banner">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <h2 class="mb-2">Ready to streamline campus event operations?</h2>
                <p class="subtle-text mb-0">
                    Centralize event creation, approvals, registration workflow, and attendance management in one modern platform.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-lg-end">
                <a asp-controller="Events" asp-action="ApprovedEvents" class="btn btn-light">
                    Explore Events
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>